OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHeavy drinkers told to     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fleave India police force   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Officials in the Indian state of Assam 
OL,6, are asking about 300 police officers   
OL,7, who they deem to have an alcohol       
OL,8, problem to quit the force.             
OL,10,FState Chief Minister Himanta Biswa     
OL,11,FSarma said heavy drinking had affected 
OL,12,Ftheir health and they were being asked 
OL,13,Fto retire early.                       
OL,15,FMr Sarma had earlier vowed to "cut the 
OL,16,Fdeadwood out of the police force".     
OL,18,FSeveral Assam officers have been       
OL,19,Fsuspended for drunken outbursts while  
OL,20,Fon duty, the Times of India reports.   
